title: Can We Bear Spray You?
description: We chat with the Bitchin' Bungalow about what's happening in the Twin Cities, Mixtape Game, Dave asks his daughter if he's allowed to give her kids sugar, Favorite Musical Moments, Eric Perkin joins the show to talk about leaving Kare 11 after 25 years, Jenny is wondering if she needs bear spray for an upcoming trip, and more!
